## Description {#details}

This class represents an <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarfexpression/operation">Operation</a> in the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/expression">Expression</a>.

An <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dwarfexpression/operation">Operation</a> can be in <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/error">Error</a> state (check with <a href="#ab09f35ca6cd360908e1493ff26081c63">isError()</a>). This means that it couldn&#39;t be decoded successfully and if it is the case, all others fields contain undefined values.
